{"about_the_game":"SANCTION is a procedurally generated post-apocalyptic world where you are a prisoner sanctioned to come from the safety of your doomsday bunker to gather supplies for the community. Your freedom and your communities livelihood relies on you. Survive the desolate wasteland left by the final war.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191080/extras/desc_animated.gif?t=1729175265\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HOW TO SURVIVE</h2>In your desperate quest for survival, you must rummage through the trash piles of bygone lives\u2014abandoned heaps of leftover supplies and the desolate remains of structures that once thrived. Within this bleak hellscape, food and water, are as scarce as hope itself. But beware\u2014the lack of clean air left on the surface. Air filters are your lifelines. To replenish them, seek out supply drops, barter with merchants, or brave the fallen bodies of those who scavenged before you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191080/extras/desc_animated_2.gif?t=1729175265\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">LIFE FOUND WITHIN THE FOG</h2>Amidst the wasteland, you\u2019ll encounter factions and merchants. They seek goods, and in return, they offer supplies and equipment. Always carry a weapon for defence against the vast amount of new 'life' found upon the surface. This includes Spirit-Walkers, a lifeless body mutated by the chemical warfare that took place many years ago. These creatures have adapted to grow wings and can terraform the earth around them, be wary as they roam for sustenance such as yourself.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Garbage Day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1191080/2a8cb034b808c857c026227ebf3944ad13cfd827.jpg"},{"name":"Dumpster Diver","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1191080/2a8cb034b808c857c026227eb